#### 安装

```shell
cd /usr/src
git clone https://github.com/FFmpeg/FFmpeg.git
cd ffmpeg
sudo ./configure --arch=armel --target-os=linux --enable-gpl --enable-libx264 --enable-nonfree
make
sudo make install
```

#### ogv to mp4


```shell
ffmpeg -i out.ogv -vcodec h264 out.mp4
```

